response.original_title: Alex Elkin: Under 30 Need Not Apply
response.overview: Taking on McDonald's, Trump and the millennial generation, Alex Elkin is a voice of reason in a world turned upside down by trigger warnings and micro aggressions. Sit back and enjoy a front row seat into the mind of a comedic "truth"sayer. Watch this rising star as he rockets his way to becoming one of America's most influential comedians of our generation.
response.title: Alex Elkin: Under 30 Need Not Apply
